Following Erica’s disqualification on Sunday, Kiddwaya has disclosed his plans for his House sweetheart. The billionaire son said he would help the rising actress in any way he can when he is out of the show. Erica was disqualified for disobeying Biggie’s rules and threatening a fellow Housemate among other violations. Speaking to Trickytee, Kidd said: I dey miss this girl small sha….I miss her a lot. When I see her face it makes me happy and the way she used to come to sit on my laps. “I know very well that for sure when I’m done here, I’ll help her any way I can.”